# moomoo OpenD credentials for the tms-live node (mounted as an env_file).
#
# For P5 MARKET-DATA + signal mode against a LOCAL OpenD (127.0.0.1:11111 on the
# host, encrypt=off) NO credentials are required — this file may be left absent.
# These knobs exist for the deferred real-OpenD smoke / future paper/live (P6),
# where OpenD is logged in on the host with a real Futu/moomoo account.
#
# Copy to secrets/moomoo.env and fill in as needed. NEVER commit secrets/moomoo.env
# (it is gitignored). The values are read from the process environment and are
# NEVER logged by tms-live.

# Optional RSA private-key path for OpenD encrypted transport (only if OpenD is
# configured with encryption; localhost market-data uses encrypt=off).
# TMS_MOOMOO_RSA_KEY_PATH=/run/secrets/opend_rsa.pem

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# P6 paper/live trading. SECRETS — set here only. Broker ACCOUNTS (the account
# numbers + which is default) are USER-MANAGED in the UI (tms.accounts) — they are
# NOT secrets and are NO LONGER set via env. Only the live-gate secrets live here.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# PAPER mode binds the (moomoo, paper) DEFAULT account from the UI — no secret here.

# LIVE mode (REAL MONEY) requires ALL of the following — the node refuses to
# activate live unless every one is present (locked decision 8). There is NO
# code path that places a real order without the full gate:
#   1. a REAL account created + marked default in the UI (tms.accounts);
#   2. the EXACT typed confirmation phrase below (never defaulted);
#   3. the OpenD unlock-trade password (plaintext; MD5'd before transport);
#   4. the distinct live trader id namespace (set TMS_LIVE_TRADER_ID below).
# TMS_LIVE_CONFIRM=I CONFIRM LIVE REAL MONEY TRADING TMS-LIVE-REAL-001
# TMS_MOOMOO_UNLOCK_PASSWORD=
# TMS_LIVE_TRADER_ID=TMS-LIVE-REAL-001
